2016-__-__ version v0.3.3
* add configureable timeout for answer from slaves
* simplify call option parsing code => changed the logic of parsing call parameters (made easier!)
* adjust and beautify help message
* changed default data type to hex (instead of char) - hex is always printable
* fix bug when no bus device is given
* fix: make function 'w' be equal to '6' like help message tells
* added README.md

